Tier 4 requires Claude Code authentication. Three options:

  1. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...      (pay-per-use API key)
  2. ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=...           (alternative auth token)
  3. CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=...        (long-lived OAuth — generate with `claude setup-token`,
                                          uses your Pro/Max
                                          subscription quota)
  4. `claude /login` (keychain session — only works
     when --tier4-bare={auto,never})
